channel.title: PhyscoDev v1, the beginning of my new server
channel.description:
Hello, this is PhyscoDev V1 :) i am using hamachi to host. But never mind that right now, i wanna show u progress as I build my server, if you're at all interested. I'll have you know I InfDev'ed the resources, but built it without ANY mods. Myself. Soo annoying.. haha. I had to flatten the land, build a ton of blocks in air, place down 5000 SQ feet of obsidian, mine the obsidian that i accidentally placed above where i wanted it, But I have the base done and I can start on the actual city now. And I want advice/criticism from you guys.
[IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/xkp37q.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i51.tinypic.com/jsd5c7.png[/img]
[IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/20scetv.png[/img]

item.description:
@walkineagle wrote:

Alriight so about plugins for my server, whaddaya think about these?

AutoBroadcast (for messages)
Permissons
SimpleHome (Home, sethome)
CreeperTNTNerf (explosion disable)
Disarm (Delete TNT with right click)
PlgSetspawn_21 (Setspawn, spawn)
properTime (make sure days and nights dont lag)
vPlayersOnline (Show online players)
